    • Uses of Event in events

      Subclasses of Event in events 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  EnterIs
      Checks if the vehicle can enter the specified intersection and if so, removes the vehicle from the road, adds it to the intersection, and enqueues an ExitIs event object.
      class  EnterIsFromParking
      Gets a vehicle from the parking lot connected to the intersection and if the vehicle can enter the first road on its path, adds the vehicle to the road and enqueues another EnterIsFromParking object.
      class  ExitIs
      Removes the vehicle from the intersection, adds it to the next road on its path and schedules an EnterIs event for the next intersection Notifies the road that was left that a vehicle exited the intersection.
      class  SwitchIsMode
      Changes the intersection mode and if the intersection is not idle, enqueues a second SwitchIsMode object
